\id NEH id NEH Matupi Chin Standard Bible (MCSB)
\h NEHEMIAH
\toc1 NEHEMIAH
\toc2 Nehemiah
\toc3 Neh
\mt1 NEHEMIAH
\mt2 (The Book of Nehemiah)
\is1 Nehemiah Cabu Kawng
\im A cuekca vaengah Ezra neh Nehemiah he pakhat la om. He rhoi dongah he Pathen pilnam rhoek Babylon vangsawn lamloh a mael vaengkah, bawkim koep a saknah, Jerusalem a thohnah, amamih Pathen olkhueng dogla a kunnah kawng a tael. Aboel parhuk hil he Ezea loh vangsawn lamkah pilnam a maelnah kawng, Jerusalem ah hmueihtuk a saknah kawng, \nd Boeipa\nd* kongaih la hmueih a nawn lamhmanah kawng a tael. Nehemiah loh Persian manghai Artaxerxes taengah boei a bi dae, Babylon vangsawn lamloh Jerusalem la aka mael pilnam kah a patangnah te a ming. Jerusalem khopuei vongka kaw boeih a hoeh uh tih vongtung khaw boeih rhawp coeng. Pathen taengah rhenah neh hoihaengnah ham a bih. Jerusalem kah khoboei bi ham neh khopuei koep sak ham khaw Artaxerxes taengah a bih thai. Tolrhum khoboei rhoek loh amah tloelh mai cakhaw hlang boeih a cului thai tih khopuei vongka neh vongtung khaw koep a thoh uh. Ezra loh pilnam hamla Moses olkhueng a tae pah, te vaengah tholh a phong uh, tun thangthui uh, boeipa kah khotue khaw koep a saii uh. Nehemiah long he thinom la bi a saii, Judah kah bawknah khaw pan a tlaih. Khlongnu khaw boeih a tueih, olkhueng loh a thui bangla Sabath khaw koep a tuem uh. Ezra neh Nehemiah cabu he 300 \sc b.c \sc* tluk vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 I. Vongtung thohnah\ior 1.1—7.70\ior*
\io2 A. A hmuethma sawtletnah\ior 1.1—2.20\ior*
\io2 B. Imsak tongnah \ior 3.1—6.19\ior*
\io2 C. Hlangmi soepnah\ior 7.1—7.70\ior*
\io1 II. Bawknah tlaivongnah \ior 8.1—13.31\ior*
\io2 A. Paipi koep thoelhnah \ior 8.1—10.39\ior*
\io2 B. Pilnam tlaihvongnah \ior 11.1—13.13\ior*
\io2 C. A tlaihvong bingbonah \ior 13.14-31\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Jerusalem Lamkah Olthang
\p 
